{{Infobox person | name = Willi Liebherr | birth_date = 1947 | education = [[ETH Zurich]] | occupation = Chairman of the board of [[Liebherr Group]] }}
'''Willi Liebherr''' (Born in 1947) is a [[Germany|German]]-[[Switzerland|Swiss]] [[Entrepreneurship|entrepreneur]] chairman of the board of [[Liebherr Group]].
== Life == Willi Liebherr grew up in [[Upper Swabia]]'s, [[Kirchdorf an der Iller]] and in [[Biberach an der Riss|Biberach]]. After graduating from the [[ETH Zurich|Swiss Federal Institute of Technology in Zurich]] as engineer, he joined the family business, [[Liebherr Group]]. Since the death of Hans Liebherr in 1993, he leads the construction machinery manufacturer together with his sister [[Isolde Liebherr|Isolde]]. Since 1999, he is the chairman of the board of Liebherr-International AG in [[Bulle]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.schwaebische.de/wirtschaft/aktuelle-nachrichten_artikel,-Liebherr-Wir-fuehlen-uns-ueberall-zu-Hause-_arid,4071197.html |title=Liebherr: "Wir fühlen uns überall zu Hause" |date=22 March 2010 |publisher=Schwäbische Zeitung |access-date=4 December 2017}}</ref>
== Honors == * [[Honorary degree|Honorary]] doctorate from the [[University of Fribourg|University of Freiburg]], 2006<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vertikal.net/de/news/artikel/3297/ |title=Ehrendoktor für Willi Liebherr |date=28 November 2006 |publisher=Vertikal Press |access-date=4 December 2017}}</ref> * Chevalier of the [[Legion of Honour]], 2010<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.liebherr.com/de/deu/%C3%BCber-liebherr/unternehmensprofil/gesellschafter/vita-willi-liebherr/willi-liebherr.html |title=Dr. h.c. Dipl.-Ing. (ETH) Willi Liebherr |publisher=Liebherr |access-date=4 December 2017}}</ref>
== Assets == On the [[Forbes]] list 2015, the wealth of Willi Liebherr was stated to be approximately US$6.1 billion. Placing him fourth in Switzerland and 240th on the Forbes list of the richest people in the world.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://amp.blick.ch/news/wirtschaft/forbes-liste-enthuellt-so-reich-sind-die-blocher-kinder-id3536360.html |title=So reich sind die Blocher-Kinder |date=4 March 2015 |publisher=Blick |access-date=4 December 2017}}</ref>
